OL,3,C1,000 people urge rail bosses to close
OL,4,Clevel crossing after tragic train crash
OL,6,FMore than 1,000 people have put their
OL,7,Fnames to a petition urging rail bosses
OL,8,Fto close a level crossing after a
OL,9,Ftragic train crash.
OL,11,FThe scene of a fatal collision
OL,12,Finvolving a train and a car on June
OL,13,F25th 2026 claimed the life of 33-year-
OL,14,Fold social worker Kerry Coombes.
OL,16,FAn eight-year-old girl, who was also
OL,17,Fin the car alongside her remains in a
OL,18,Fcritical but stable condition in
OL,19,Fhospital, British Transport Police
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
