OL,3,C1,000 people urge rail bosses to close
OL,4,Clevel crossing after tragic train crash
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,7,Fcrossing after the 07.51 Northern
OL,8,FTrain service from Colne to Preston.
OL,10,FKerry's family said: "Kerry was a
OL,11,Floving daughter, sister, partner and
OL,12,Fdevoted mum who meant everything to us.
OL,14,F"She had the biggest heart, always put
OL,15,Fother people before herself and
OL,16,Fbrought so much love, laughter and
OL,17,Fkindness into the lives of everyone
OL,18,Fwho knew her.
OL,26,@rD@VOU
