PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784130494
OL,3,C1,000 people urge rail bosses to close
OL,4,Clevel crossing after tragic train crash
OL,6,F"The loss of Kerry has left a hole in
OL,7,Four family that can never be filled.
OL,8,FWe are heartbroken and are trying to
OL,9,Fcome to terms with what has happened."
OL,11,FAn online petition urges Network Rail
OL,12,Fand Lancashire County Council to
OL,13,Fpermanently close the Station Road
OL,14,Fcrossing and redirect traffic via the
OL,15,FA675, nearby.
OL,17,FCampaigners say it's about preventing
OL,18,Fanother family from experiencing the
OL,19,Funimaginable - and have asked people
OL,20,Fto sign their petition to support a
OL,21,Fsafer future for the area.
OL,26,@qD@fO]
